name: Can't Fake The Fitment - VIP Parking
description:
- Can't Fake The Fitment -

  Saturday June 29th 2013

60 Acres Park - Redmond, WA

No matter your style: Form or Function, it's all about The Fitment.  Stanced or functional, track or street, you can't fake it: your fitment says it all. So, what do you have to say?  Come to the only show where YOU decide the King (or Queen) of Fitment in the NW!  Admission price includes a ballot where YOU decide who takes the trophy home!

VIP Roll in times are 11:00AM-12:00PM!

Item price of $8.00 includes:
1 VIP Parking Pass(sticker MUST be fit to driver's side of windshield to be valid). 
1 Driver  Admission to CFTF (Bracelet and Ballot).
1 Passenger Admission to CFTF (Bracelet and Ballot).
1 Sticker Packet


 VIP Parking also includes admission for Driver and 1 Passenger, (two voting ballots and two wristbands), as well as sticker pack. The car show will proceed rain or shine. No refunds will be given. 
Please print your paypal receipt and bring it with you! We will have a list of the entries but in the rare chance that an error has occurred you will have your receipt!


Emailed instructions will be coming soon for:

-Roll in times
-Where to enter
-Rules

Also, look for more info soon about music, vendors, food and more!

name: Can't Fake The Fitment - Showcar Entry
description:
- Can't Fake The Fitment -

  Saturday June 29th 2013

60 Acres Park Redmond, WA

No matter your style: Form or Function, it's all about The Fitment.  Stanced or functional, track or street, you can't fake it: your fitment says it all. So, what do you have to say?  Come to the only show where YOU decide the King (or Queen) of Fitment in the NW!  Admission price includes a ballot where YOU decide who takes the trophy home!

Can't Fake the Fitment is about what YOUR fitment is. We have 15 categories to compete in. The first two are our spectator judged categories. As you enter the event with general admission, you'll be handed a ballot. In two categories, YOU will help pick the winners for:
1. Best Functional Fitment!
2. Best Stance and Form! 

In the following categories, our judges will select the winners of:

3. Best Street Savage
4. Best Track Machine
5. Best Drift-All-Day
6. Best Bags-Gone-Wild
7. Best Static Soldier
8. Best Crew Quality
9. Best Old School Flavor JDM
10. Best Old School Flavor EURO
11. Best VIP Fitment
12. Best JDM Fitment
13. Best EURO Fitment
14. Best USDM Fitment
15. Best Two-Wheel Motion (Scooters)

Item price of $15.00 includes:
1 Vehicle Entry to CFTF Car Show. 
1 Driver  Admission to CFTF (Bracelet and Ballot).
1 Passenger Admission to CFTF (Bracelet and Ballot).
1 Sticker Packet


 Showcar Entry also includes admission for Driver and 1 Passenger, (two voting ballots and two wristbands), as well as sticker pack. The car show will proceed rain or shine. No refunds will be given. If you are unsure that you can make the event please hold off on your registration. Please print your paypal receipt and bring it with you! We will have a list of the entries but in the rare chance that an error has occurred you will have your receipt!

Emailed instructions will be coming soon for:

-Roll in times
-Where to enter
-Rules


Also, look for more info soon about music, vendors, food and more!

name: Farmofminds X Ben Sopra GT-R Tee
description: Farmofminds and Ben Sopra bring you the "BIG BOSS" GT-R tee. This high-quality print tee features the famous Ben Sopra R35 GT-R. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL and XXL for a limited time from CFTF! Packaged in the Ben Sopra collectible tube.
